nfo can others see?","#-hcdhg4":"Your visibility settings are saved in SharePoint. To view your visibility settings, {0}.","#47agvb":"go to SharePoint","#-bnt3p1":"How do I choose what Microsoft 365 profile info others can see?","#dkrn1v":"Download your profile data","#-g10hmz":"Edit your profile in Microsoft 365","#-52xgen":"Microsoft privacy statement","#afziwy":"Profile cards in Microsoft","#ew9ypj":"Learn more about pronouns","#2w9oyv":"See also","#63y3aw":"When on, AI automatically generates a skills profile for you based on your role and work activity in Microsoft 365. New skills are added regularly to help you easily share a current view of your capabilities with your organization. When off, AI won’t add skills to your profile.","#le3pa":"Learn about how AI identifies your skills","#ijjo2c":"Allow AI to add skills to your profile","#-umt870":"Update your skills settings","#ccb2vu":"Choose which profile info others can see (except skills) in SharePoint. To manage who can see your skills, go to {0} on this page. {1}","#-ummypz":"Go to SharePoint","#-713i3d":"When on, people in your organization can see your skills in places like your profile card to help you easily connect with others and share your expertise. When off, only you can see your skills.","#uimlab":"Share your skills on your profile","#-3u3ify":"To save time, share AI-added and imported skills automatically.","#u7awdd":"To save time, share AI-added skills automatically.","#-1xbdgc":"When on, AI-added skills are shared automatically with others, making it effortless to keep your skills up to date. When off, only you can see these skills until you confirm them.","#-awlwu8":"Share AI-added skills automatically","#-7qmtzq":"When on, if an admin in your organization imports skills from sources like an existing profile they are shared automatically with others. When off, only you can see these skills until you confirm them.","#d9tp52":"Share imported skills automatically","#-7ng48s":"Update your skills settings","#-j04ari":"To show AI-added skills automatically, you must first allow AI to add skills to your profile.","#z0va5j":"To show imported skills automatically, you must first choose to share skills on your profile.","#6k9ksr":"To show AI-added skills automatically, you must first choose to share skills on your profile.","#-p3qxxs":"To show AI-added and imported skills automatically, you must first choose to show skills on your profile.","#-tjsjit":"When on, AI automatically identifies tasks you frequently work on based on your activity in Microsoft 365. This helps Copilot suggest ways to use AI to support your everyday work and helps your organization understand where AI can be most useful. When off, AI won't identify your tasks.","#t10p0r":"Learn more about AI-identified tasks and what data they use","#-negoqh":"Allow AI to identify your tasks","#k9ywm7":"When on, your AI-identified tasks are included in aggregated data used by Microsoft 365 Copilot and select Copilot agents. This helps leaders understand how people across the organization can use AI. When off, your AI-identified tasks aren't included in this aggregated data.","#-bvuth":"Share AI-identified tasks automatically","#-t94gsc":"Update your tasks settings","#-yhgq2":"To share AI-added tasks automatically, you must first allow AI to identify your tasks.","#-x1dmp2":"Close","#snu0xg":"Close","#-7o4im2":"Keep editing","#124sxd":"If you leave now your changes won't be saved.","#wu7dlg":"You have unsaved changes","#b70vay":"Display name","#-jafj6t":"Enter your display name","#21mbxn":"Edit your profile","#7pbcl7":"Work email","#-6tirqp":"Email","#h5y7es":"Something went wrong.","#-q5uqbc":"Please close this window and try again.","#-mtmm6n":"Add an interest or hobby, press enter to submit","#-h3zt3i":"Interests and hobbies","#4151al":"interests","#-bfd4kt":"At least one interest or hobby is required","#-jfwszy":"Add interests and hobbies","#86hawn":"{0}, press enter to remove","#-b6qzn9":"Fetching profil